The paper deals with the deployment of wireless networks and communication between nodes, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The use of beeps as a means of communication and the limited knowledge and capabilities of nodes suggest that the paper may also belong to the categories of distributed, parallel, and cooperative computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), and systems and control (cs.SY).
